Paper: hep-th/0101124

Date: 2001-01-18

Title: Supersymmetry in Classical Mechanics

Authors: E.Deotto, E.Gozzi, D.Mauro

Comments: Review article submitted to the "Concise Encyclopaedia of Susy"

We briefly review the universal supersymmetry present in classicalhamiltonian systems and show its applications to field theories.